#: ../../spinningup/exercise2_1_soln.rst:8
msgid ""
"Learning curves for TRPO in Hopper-v2 with different values of "
"``train_v_iters``, averaged over three random seeds."
msgstr ""
"TRPO 在 Hopper-v2 環境中使用不同 ``train_v_iters`` 值的學習曲線，"
"結果為三個隨機種子的平均值。"

#: ../../spinningup/exercise2_1_soln.rst:11
msgid ""
"The difference is quite substantial: with a trained value function, the "
"agent is able to quickly make progress. With an untrained value function,"
" the agent gets stuck early on."
msgstr ""
"差異相當顯著：使用訓練過的價值函數（value function）時，智慧體（agent）能夠快速取得進展。"
"而使用未訓練的價值函數時，智慧體在早期就會陷入停滯。"
